org.apache.karaf.features.internal.service

Interface BundleInstallSupport

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AssemblyDeployCallback, BundleInstallSupportImpl, StaticInstallSupport

    public interface BundleInstallSupport

    Interface to interact with OSGi framework.

    Bundles are installed into regions and features are used only to get their configs and libraries.

Shall be called with Bundle.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  BundleInstallSupport.FrameworkInfo
      Low-level state of system, provides information about start levels (initial and current), system bundle, bundle of features service and entire map of bundle IDs to Bundle instances.
